  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as the boy named HERO in this thrilling anime-inspired Beat Em Up game. beat everyone in the school and save your beloved girlfriend! this game have everything! nice story, cool anime style cutscenes, and a lot of punches and kicks!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2871290/extras/060a8e0ab42030affd97e0ae1d053b45.poster.avif?t=1749555887\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2871290/extras/060a8e0ab42030affd97e0ae1d053b45.webm?t=1749555887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2871290/extras/060a8e0ab42030affd97e0ae1d053b45.mp4?t=1749555887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the new kid in school, you find yourself entangled in a web of dark conspiracies when a malevolent group kidnaps your beloved girlfriend. Armed with martial arts prowess and an unyielding determination, dive into action to save her from the clutches of evil.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2871290/extras/05c3a1a9104a1ec7cec1af9d85276b95.poster.avif?t=1749555887\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2871290/extras/05c3a1a9104a1ec7cec1af9d85276b95.webm?t=1749555887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2871290/extras/05c3a1a9104a1ec7cec1af9d85276b95.mp4?t=1749555887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Story mode - Arcade mode or Survival mode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-</strong> Interesting story line with cool anime cutscenes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-</strong> Stunning pixel art mixed with anime to give a unique modern blend of arcade-style action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-</strong> Multiple levels with cool colorful backgrounds to battle your way through.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-</strong> Many weapons to grab, Many enemies to beat! you can grab and throw them too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-</strong> XP SYSTEM to level up your HERO to become POWERFULL! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-</strong> Shop to buy 1up, experiense, energy or health!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-</strong> Classic arcade beat-‘em-up gameplay with so many new mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-</strong> Choose Difficulty</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unlock Cute Pets s support in battle!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2871290/extras/85eb471afbf4b3e42f09a5a6b575fbbe.poster.avif?t=1749555887\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2871290/extras/85eb471afbf4b3e42f09a5a6b575fbbe.webm?t=1749555887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2871290/extras/85eb471afbf4b3e42f09a5a6b575fbbe.mp4?t=1749555887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as the boy named HERO in this thrilling anime-inspired Beat Em Up game. beat everyone in the school and save your beloved girlfriend! this game have everything! nice story, cool anime style cutscenes, and a lot of punches and kicks!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2871290/extras/060a8e0ab42030affd97e0ae1d053b45.poster.avif?t=1749555887\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2871290/extras/060a8e0ab42030affd97e0ae1d053b45.webm?t=1749555887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2871290/extras/060a8e0ab42030affd97e0ae1d053b45.mp4?t=1749555887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the new kid in school, you find yourself entangled in a web of dark conspiracies when a malevolent group kidnaps your beloved girlfriend. Armed with martial arts prowess and an unyielding determination, dive into action to save her from the clutches of evil.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2871290/extras/05c3a1a9104a1ec7cec1af9d85276b95.poster.avif?t=1749555887\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2871290/extras/05c3a1a9104a1ec7cec1af9d85276b95.webm?t=1749555887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2871290/extras/05c3a1a9104a1ec7cec1af9d85276b95.mp4?t=1749555887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Story mode - Arcade mode or Survival mode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-</strong> Interesting story line with cool anime cutscenes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-</strong> Stunning pixel art mixed with anime to give a unique modern blend of arcade-style action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-</strong> Multiple levels with cool colorful backgrounds to battle your way through.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-</strong> Many weapons to grab, Many enemies to beat! you can grab and throw them too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-</strong> XP SYSTEM to level up your HERO to become POWERFULL! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-</strong> Shop to buy 1up, experiense, energy or health!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-</strong> Classic arcade beat-‘em-up gameplay with so many new mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-</strong> Choose Difficulty</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unlock Cute Pets s support in battle!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2871290/extras/85eb471afbf4b3e42f09a5a6b575fbbe.poster.avif?t=1749555887\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2871290/extras/85eb471afbf4b3e42f09a5a6b575fbbe.webm?t=1749555887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2871290/extras/85eb471afbf4b3e42f09a5a6b575fbbe.mp4?t=1749555887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
